<CENTER><FONT FACE=Helvetica,arial SIZE=5><BR>
<B>HOW TO JOIN THE GUILD</B></CENTER></FONT>

<FONT FACE=Helvetica,arial SIZE=3><P>
We've had a lot of requests to join the guild even though we're still defining the charter!  This is a great time to join, since you can help us define the guild and its concepts.
<P>
At this time, we are accepting applications from any enchanter in EverQuest.  Since we're in the formative stage of the guild, all applicants will be accepted into the guild as members immediately.  The only requirement for membership is that you are an enchanter and you follow the tenets of the guild, which will be defined in our charter.
<P>
Applying is easy.  Click the 'APPLY' button on the left hand menu bar and fill out the form.  You will immediately be granted full access to the members-only section of the website and your application will be processed as soon as possible.
<P>
Welcome to the guild!


